OL,3,CMan damaged 'every panel' of BMW after
OL,4,Cowner displayed Palestinian flag
OL,6,FA man has been sentenced for damaging
OL,7,Fcars and a garden wall after seeing
OL,8,FPalestinian flags displayed in the
OL,9,Fowners' windows.
OL,11,FElliot Kersh admitted he carried out
OL,12,Fthe damage while on late night walks
OL,13,Fwith his dog in between October and
OL,14,FDecember 2023.
OL,16,FThe incidents included scratching a
OL,17,FBMW along the front, side, and rear of
OL,18,Fthe car. Over the next few weeks, the
OL,19,Fowner of the car discovered further
OL,20,Fdamage.
