OL,3,CMan damaged 'every panel' of BMW after
OL,4,Cowner displayed Palestinian flag
OL,6,FBy 6 December, almost every panel had
OL,7,Fbeen badly scratched.
OL,9,FThe 64-year-old also spray painted a
OL,10,Fgarden wall and scratched the bonnet
OL,11,Fof a VW Golf on a nearby road.
OL,13,FThe owners of both cars had
OL,14,FPalestinian flags in their windows.
OL,16,FAfter being arrested, Kersh admitted
OL,17,Fto damaging both cars and the garden
OL,18,Fwall, claiming he found the flags
OL,19,Foffensive and intimidating - but said
OL,20,Fhe was not racist.
