OL,3,CMan damaged 'every panel' of BMW after
OL,4,Cowner displayed Palestinian flag
OL,6,FKersh went on to appear atMagistrates
OL,7,FCourt in December 2023, where he
OL,8,Fpleaded guilty to three charges of
OL,9,Fracially aggravated criminal damage.
OL,11,FKersh was sentenced to a 12 month
OL,12,FCommunity Order with 15 Rehabilitation
OL,13,FDays and the court imposed a 12 month
OL,14,FRestraining Order.
OL,16,FHe was also ordered him to carry out
OL,17,F60 hours unpaid work.
