OL,3,CMan damaged 'every panel' of BMW after
OL,4,Cowner displayed Palestinian flag
OL,6,FJoseph Seale, Senior Crown Prosecutor
OL,7,Ffor CPS North West, said: "Elliott
OL,8,FKersh has caused considerable upset
OL,9,Fand fear by deliberately targeting
OL,10,Fproperty belonging to homeowners who
OL,11,Fhad Palestinian flags displayed in
OL,12,Ftheir windows.
OL,14,F"The CPS take incidents of hate crime
OL,15,Fvery seriously and we are dedicated to
OL,16,Fbringing perpetrators to justice,
OL,17,Fwhich is why we asked the court to
OL,18,Fapply an uplift to Kersh's sentence to
OL,19,Freflect the racial aggravation of the
OL,20,Foffences he committed.
